org.deeplearning4j.plot

Class BarnesHutTsne

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.deeplearning4j.plot.BarnesHutTsne
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model

    public class BarnesHutTsne
extends java.lang.Object
implements Model
    Barnes hut algorithm for TSNE, uses a dual tree approximation approach. Work based on: http://lvdmaaten.github.io/tsne/ For hight dimensions, it's recommended to reduce the dimension up to 50 using another method (PCA or other)
